{"tid":898503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大佬啊 曼城身價最球最貴 嬴曼聯好合理姐","createTime":"2018-11-11T17:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T17:35:15.000Z","uid":46013,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"17b8daa44f2354533df72eae6b8f450621c75f33","tid":898503,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"瑞士的足球研究機構 CIES Football Observatory 周一公佈，曼城現役球員陣容身價高達8.78億歐元（約84.37億港元），是歷來身價最貴的球隊。<br />\n1月在冬季轉會窗以6,500萬歐元轉會由畢爾包羅致了法國中堅拿樸迪的曼城，現役球員陣容價值為8.78億歐元，是身價最貴球隊，巴黎聖日耳門（PSG）以8.05億歐元排第二，第三位是7.47億歐元的曼聯，巴塞隆拿和皇家馬德里則分別以7.25億歐元和4.97億歐元，排在第四和第六位。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯先排第3 憑咩嬴曼城啊? 嬴祖記就話易姐"},{"pid":"b1a5a0ea68ff74c13dc344f703f28a6dfdd02306","tid":898503,"uid":161731,"like":11,"dislike":13,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"係 有時覺得拎曼聯同曼城比真係好on9"},{"pid":"64b64f690e70b12bd01904e8105bfd2819140085","tid":898503,"uid":43557,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"輸真系好正常"},{"pid":"30f27ae18ca7076c166056d629ac2aeb7f03bbd0","tid":898503,"uid":31423,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過身價係嚟到曼城之後先升<br />\n曼聯可能係跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864fd2b1ff637c575c3167e4fcc003f6ea3e86c6","tid":898503,"uid":46013,"like":12,"dislike":35,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"30f27ae18ca7076c166056d629ac2aeb7f03bbd0","tid":898503,"uid":31423,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過身價係嚟到曼城之後先升<br />\n曼聯可能係跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"大佬 果陣買番黎都粒粒巨星啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曼聯玩開自家青訓出品都有7億幾 算係咁啦"},{"pid":"74bda9f7a742eebb791b8f11340086542f877fa9","tid":898503,"uid":59357,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"曼聯身價夠係狼隊十倍 <img src=\"/a